desc: Home décor boutique offering a curated selection of unique and on-trend items to enhance and delight home life.

layout.text: I'm Julie, and I started this online home boutique to share my favorite home décor finds with those who love them too. I am a one-woman show in Colorado, so the satisfaction of my customers means everything to me! Thank you so much for being here. Please shop around, DM me if your heart desires, and have some fun...Welcome to the new boutique!
